reviewText: Really good videos. Lots of Sierra scenery. Really cool snow removal video.
The four SD40T-2's throttling up in the snow alone is worth the price. Crank it up! Love Richard as a guest narrator.
Very exciting to see this challenging battle against snow that won't stop. These snow fighting railroad men must have a special gene. Five stars for them and Pentrex on this one.
If you are a Southern Pacific Fan this is a must for your dvd collection. After order was placed I had it in a matter of days
